description:
The second collection of all-color Sunday Big Nate cartoons!

Life can be stressful for Nate Wright. At school, Mrs. Godfrey makes every day a nightmare. At home, he's stuck between Ellen, his incredibly annoying older sister, and Dad, perhaps the most clueless parent of all time. And don't get him started on Gina, the ultimate teacher's pet, or Artur, the unassuming exchange student who bests him at every turn. It's enough to make even a can-do kid like Nate scream: "I CAN'T TAKE IT!"
name: GN

volume.name: Big Nate: I Can't Take It!

description:
Meet Desmond Pucket--professor of frightology and master of monsters.

Someday Desmond will be famous for his special effects wizardry, but for now he's just trying to make it through sixth grade at Cloverfield Memorial Junior High, which means he needs to stay one step ahead of the school's disciplinary officer, Mr. Needles.

The only problem is Desmond just can't stop pulling pranks--like the time he attached a shrieking rubber goblin to the toilet seat in the teachers' bathroom. Mrs. Rubin screamed so loudly her wig flew off! Or the time he put giant motorized worms into the mashed potatoes in the cafeteria. Or the time Desmond and his best friend, Ricky, arranged for a three-headed ghost to crash his sister's slumber party. Rachel still hasn't forgiven him.

And now Desmond has to stay prank-free for the rest of the year, or he won't be able to go on the class trip to Crab Shell Pier, home of the Mountain Full of Monsters ride! It's going to be tough, but Desmond has to try.

This book includes a section of "Desmond's Notes": instructions for making monster magic (think scary noises, or fake blood) at home!
name: GN

description:
Matthew Inman's first collection of The Oatmeal.com spent six weeks on the New York Times bestseller list and sold 200,000 copies. This pivotal and influential comic collection titled 5 Very Good Reasons to Punch a Dolphin in the Mouth introduced Samurai sword-wielding kittens and informed us on how to tell if a velociraptor is having pre-marital sex. Matthew's cat-themed collection How to Tell If Your Cat Is Plotting to Kill You is a #1 New York Times bestseller with more than half a million copies in print. Now with Why Grizzly Bears Should Wear Underpants, Inman offers a delicious, tantalizing follow-up featuring all new material that has been posted on the site since the publication of the first book plus never-before-seen comics that have not appeared anywhere. As with every Oatmeal collection, there is a pull-out poster at the back of the book.

In this second collection of over 50 comics, you'll be treated to the hilarity of "The Crap We Put Up with Getting On and Off an Airplane," "Why Captain Higgins Is My Favorite Parasitic Flatworm," "This Is How I Feel about Buying Apps," "6 Things You Really Don't Need to Take a Photo of," and much more. Along with lambasting the latest culture crazes, Inman serves up recurrent themes such as foodstuffs, holidays, e-mail, as well as technological, news-of-the-day, and his snarky yet informative comics on grammar and usage. Online and in print, The Oatmeal delivers brilliant, irreverent comic hilarity.
name: GN

volume.name: Why Grizzly Bears Should Wear Underpants

deck: The war between Saint-Ange and FEAH is culminating.
description:
During the final of the previous volume, the team of Ange had to flee the underworld and left the gates open. Now the city is flooded with demons and ghosts. Furthermore they had to leave Claidheamor behind.

Funerailles decides to split up the teams. His team will go down to the underworld to rescue Claidheamor. Another team headed by Scipio need to search for Ombre and Xiong Mao, who are on a romantic outing and have not recovered their memory. Xiong Mao is needed to repair a sword. The other heroes have to protect the people of the city against the beings from the underworld. Lynette is charged with coordinating all actions. The romantic outing of Ombre and Xiong Mao quickly turns into a nightmare. Meanwhile Funerailles and his team have to battle a way down the seven levels of the underworld. A lot is learned of the past of several of the involved heroes. The dean of Saint Ange is once again plotting against FEAH and tries to blame them for the outbreak of the monsters.
name: Clémentine

description:
GAME ON!

The anti-social members of the Neighbors Club waste their time playing bishoujo games, playacting, and getting into arguments about the geekiest things. Yet somehow they've managed to add seven members to their pathetic ranks.

Whether it's writing a round robin short story together-a seemingly innocent affair until someone goes berserk-or taking things too far in an MMORPG, these freaks take their fantasy seriously. But can a group of people so alienated from the rest of the world really make friends with each?

Chapter Titles

  • Club Activity Log 16: The Story of Saint Aniki-san
  • Club Activity Log 17: Romancing Saga Prefecture (Part One)
  • Club Activity Log 18: Romancing Saga Prefecture (Part Two)
  • Club Activity Log 19: Karaoke
  • Club Activity Log 20: The Unfortunate Club

Note: The digital edition (10/2/2013) for this volume was released two weeks before the print edition (10/16/2013).

volume.name: Haganai: I Don't Have Many Friends

description:
CIRCLE OF DEATH

It's the end...and beginning. As the tangled threads of fate tighten around Victor and Mary, Tesla and Lord Weiss, Jimmy and Irene, a new figure appears in the dark London streets. Or rather, a very old one. Who is the vampire Arsene Lupin, and how does his destiny intertwine with those of Holmes and Watson? Learn how this age-old tale of blood, death, and vengeance began, even as the story winds to a close in the final volume of Jack the Ripper: Hell Blade!

Note: The digital edition (10/2/2013) for this volume was released two weeks before the print edition (10/16/2013).
name: Vol. 5

description:
SPIN-OFF TO NEW YORK TIMES BEST SELLER DANCE IN THE VAMPIRE BUND!

The Vampire Bund, a peaceful island nation of vampires off the coast of Tokyo, ruled by Princess Mina Tepes, has seen its share of conflict and turmoil. And yet there are times of relative tranquility when the Bund is a popular tourist destination during daylight hours.

When two teenage tourists, Garcia Fujisaki and his reckless best friend Masaki, ditch their group to find a vampire who will turn Masaki, it's Garcia who pays the price. Awakening as an unwilling creature of the night, Garcia finds himself entangled with a seedy band of terrorists looking to destroy the only known cure for vampirism. Garcia must find the cure and administer it within forty-eight hours, or his condition is irreversible!

Note: The digital edition (10/2/2013) for this volume was released two weeks before the print edition (10/16/2013).
name: Vol. 1

description:
IN THE BUND, EVIL NEVER SLEEPS

It's been a few weeks since Akira Garcia got caught up in a whirlwind of events that caused him to become a servant of the night. Now a permanent resident of the Vampire Bund, his job is to do Princess Mina's dirty work. With dozens of vampires reportedly missing, Garcia finds himself skulking through a mysterious lab in search of answers that will lead down a path of no return.

The hotly-anticipated second installment of Dive in the Vampire Bund has finally arrived!

Note: The digital edition (10/2/2013) for this volume was released two weeks before the print edition (10/16/2013).

description: In a purely nostaglic mood, Marcel Kiekeboe buys a comic of Snijboon and Son, an old comic series he used to read as a young boy. He doesn't realize what he has gotten himself into. The sons of the deceased artist are in a bit of a struggle to get their hands on the comic and the Kiekeboes are stuck in the middle. Due to an invention of Nerd, the new boyfriend of Fanny, the family litterally ends up in the comic. And that much color creates much ruckus in the blue-brown world of yesteryears comic.
name: Vrouwen Komen Van Mars

description: The Kiekeboes are invited to travel to Japan. However, they are not the only ones to travel to the Far East: Mona also gets to the land of the rising sun! The famous Japanese robot specialist No How wants to use her for the top secret project Tenthousand Days, in which the Yakuza, the Japanese mob, also seems to be involved.
name: Tienduizend Dagen

description: Tomboy has bought a decaying barn in the West-Flamish county and Fanny and Alanis help her rebuilt it. As if the confrontation between Alanis and Tomboy isn't enough, the German director Sausbinder comes to shoot a war movie at the barn, for which he digs real trenches. Or has the digging machine something to do with the rumors of a hidden treasure? And has Sausbinder something to do with the sudden disappearance of Alanis, or are there other men lurking about?
name: De Pepermunten

description: It's not going well with Moemoe. In fact, it's going so bad that she must be taken care of in a home for old people with dementia. Has it got something to do with the bird flu that's holding the country in its grip? When Marcel wants to clean up the stuff of his mother, he discovers her diaries. He starts reading them and discovers a family secret that will change his life forever...
name: Omtrent Oscar

description: The Kiekeboes go to Den Haan for a weekend of sun, sea and festivities. It turns out rather different when Konstantinopel finds a rubber duckey on the beach. Soon they are chased by American and Chinese criminals. Fanny and her new love Jack fall into the hands of Sho Ping Mal, who clearly has sinister plans if they don't tell them quickly where the duckeys are. If only they knew it themselves...
name: Alle Eendjes

description: Complete chaos at the Kiekeboes! The whole street is broken up and the centre of the town is unreachable due to a great marathon. And Dede manages to escape from the Ribbedebie jail. He's still wanting revenge on Marcel Kiekebie for putting him in jail. What follows is a nerve breaking chase by truck, by speedboat and even by zeppelin!
name: Een Dagje Dede

description:
The Naked Truth

The Kiekeboes get a visit from Felix, Charlotte's prudish uncle. The man is very wealthy and the family wants to get in his favor... and his will. But then nude pictures of Fanny appear in the Playfair! Pictures which the conservative uncle Felix must not see...

The Caves Of Ann

Marcel Kiekeboe gets stuck in a precarious situation created by his boss, Van de Kasseien. He must take his place in a survival weekend in the Ardennes. But the instructors turns out to be Van der Neffe and he recognizes Marcel immediately...
name: Schatjes Op Zolder

description: A coincidental meeting on Madeira, a USB-stick with a strange French text and a mysterious babysit - more is not needed to plunge the Kiekeboes into a new adventure. Intrigues in the highest orders of the army and two old friends who bundle their criminal forces: it gets warm under the feet of Marcel and his family! Who cracks code E and averts a worldly disaster?
name: Code E
